Image provided.This annual film competition is held in conjunction with the screenings of the annual Banff Mountain Film Festival World Tour, which Cape Union Mart brings to South Africa every October. The winning film is screened at this event and the winner receives a R10,000 cash prize and K-Way gear to the value of R5,000. A panel of judges from the adventure and filmmaking industries reviews submissions received. To enter, submit the link to your five-minute short film on YouTube, submit it here. Entries close on Friday, 30 June 2017.